{"tid":1711103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單分析 如何救中大","createTime":"2019-11-12T10:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T10:07:25.000Z","uid":60032,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e57dc9fb09b97d2895f5e60e54064425950d25de","tid":1711103,"uid":60032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:00:56.000Z","msg":"聽朝仲有晨曦行動<br />\n今日你地入晒中大畀狗圍仲有乜用?？<br />\n今日入得暴大果D應該係真勇武<br />\n聽朝仲邊有人行動?<br />\n今晚應該係近近地嘅地方開下花<br />\n放工時份分散狗力先為上策<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>圍魏救趙是兵法「三十六計」的第二計。原文註釋為：「共敵不如分敵，敵陽不如敵陰。」此計之意思是：<br />\n<br />\n攻打正面強大集中之敵人，不如設法分散它而後再打；例如利用敵人之精銳正在攻打另一國家，並且兩軍相持不下時，趁機攻佔敵方本土，迫使敵人退兵或分兵；<br />\n先打擊氣勢旺盛的之敵人，不如尋找機會先打擊敵人虛弱之地方，消滅敵人。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBE WATER MY FRIEND<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KOrJxgi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKOrJxgi.png&h=52f1f8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住:唔好咁做，要守法"},{"pid":"bf46a3821709afa033a8ee8968aba9a67e66d44e","tid":1711103,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"⚠轉出去⚠<br />\n❗大學 Lab 善用化學品反抗❗<br />\n❗HNO3❗<br />\n❗Mg❗<br />\n❗NH4NO3❗<br />\n❗NaOH❗<br />\n❗ANFO❗<br />\n❗ANSU❗"},{"pid":"a49c63db8a8826bffe0caaaf156f2ac8273b5c0d","tid":1711103,"uid":60032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:01:14.000Z","msg":"001"},{"pid":"eeb6f251f3f3b4fe3acab7a1ddce9f2d29f5d8a3","tid":1711103,"uid":60032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:01:26.000Z","msg":"002"},{"pid":"00ad7d4dfd11159ec82f9c020658cc0c7ee89b80","tid":1711103,"uid":60032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:01:36.000Z","msg":"003"},{"pid":"020da5f0d7db2fe11a3beb0fe55c2c7abfbd2785","tid":1711103,"uid":60032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:01:47.000Z","msg":"004"},{"pid":"ddf625435753c2a94d90961391ddabf5b6ddf475","tid":1711103,"uid":60032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c